Marissa Mayer debunked this in 2013:
<a href="http://www.businessinsider.com/mayer-google-20-time-does-not-exist-2015-1" rel="nofollow">http://www.businessinsider.com/mayer-google-20-time-does-not...</a><p>&quot;It’s funny,&quot; she said. &quot;People have been asking me since I got here, &#x27;When is Yahoo going to have 20% time?&#x27;&quot;?
&quot;I’ve got to tell you the dirty little secret of Google’s 20% time. It’s really 120% time.&quot;
